OL,5, A ex-Met Police officer, suspended     
OL,6, after a BBC investigation revealed he  
OL,7, had been posting racist content on     
OL,8, WhatsApp, has been arrested.           
OL,10,FRob Lewis, now a Home Office official, 
OL,11,Fis being held on suspicion of offences 
OL,12,Funder the Communications Act and       
OL,13,Fmisconduct in a public office.         
OL,15,FBBC Newsnight has seen racist messages 
OL,16,Fabout flooding in Pakistan, as well as 
OL,17,FHarry and Meghan, shared in the chat.  
OL,19,FThe Home Office suspended him, calling 
OL,20,Fthe messages "vile and deplorable".    
